<package name="kraft" project="openSUSE:Factory">
  <title>KDE software to handle business documents in your small business</title>
  <description>Kraft is a free software project that helps to create office documents like offers and invoices especially for small enterprise operators such as handcrafters and othres. It is easy to use but feature rich. 

Features:
* Customer management, deeply integrated in the KDE infrastructure using KAddressbook
* Automatted creation of offers, invoices and similar documents
* Text templates for document texts and items
* A Calculation module
* Material management
* Configurable high quality document creation in PDF format
* easy to use, intuitive interface 
</description>
  <devel project="KDE:Extra" package="kraft"/>
</package>
